;'''piano''' (noun)
:Short for '''Pianoforte'''.  A keyboard musical instrument.

;'''Piano''' (adj.)
:Soft. Used in musical [[notation]] in its abbreviated form, ''{p.}'', to denote lowering the volume of the music. In the pianoforte this is done by pressing the instrument's keys more lightly. 

==Etymology==

;'''Pianoforte'''
:Italian ''Piano'' (soft) + ''forte'' (strong).